```javascript
primary: "#0097a9"    // yg_blue - primary actions, links
yg_moss: "#7A9A01"    // green accent
yg_zinc: "#24405A"    // dark blue
yg_twilight: "#512A44" // purple accent
yg_lichen: "#DC4405"  // orange accent
yg_sun: "#F2A900"     // yellow accent
```

